		<p dir="LTR"><b><u><font color="#FF9933" face="Tahoma">Project 
		Motivation/Objectives</font></u></b></p>
		<p dir="LTR" align="left"><b><font color="#375294">The&nbsp; proposal of the 
		Project&nbsp; is to upgrade the Infrastructure of the Information &amp; Link 
		Network (ILN) of the Menoufiya University and its branches distributed 
		at Shebin El-Kom City, Menouf City, Ashemon City and El-Sadat City, 
		Menoufiya Government.</font></b></p>
		<p class="MsoNormal" dir="LTR" style="text-align: left; text-kashida: 0%; text-indent: 36.0pt; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed">
		<b><font color="#375294">The following Figure 1 illustrates the complete 
		&nbsp;configuration of the Information &amp; Link Network (ILN) of the Menoufiya 
		University and its branches, which will be the same except the 
		replacement of the equipments which anticipated the increase in Internet 
		B.W., also the connection of the new branches with the same topology of 
		the hole network.</font></b></p>
		<p class="MsoNormal" dir="LTR" style="text-align: left; text-kashida: 0%; text-indent: 36.0pt; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed">
