		<p class="MsoNormal" align="center" dir="LTR" style="text-align: left; line-height: 150%; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed">
		<b><font color="#FF9933">Figure 1 The complete &nbsp;configuration of the 
		Information &amp; Link Network (ILN) of the Menoufiya University and its 
		branches.</font></b></p>
		<p class="MsoNormal" dir="LTR" style="text-align: justify; text-kashida: 0%; line-height: 150%; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed">
		<b><font color="#375294">&nbsp;</font></b></p>
		<p class="MsoNormal" dir="LTR" style="text-align: justify; text-kashida: 0%; text-indent: 57.6pt; line-height: 150%; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed">
		<b><font color="#375294">However, there are new Faculties, Institutes, 
		and Centers have been established and are not yet connect to the 
		Internet, therefore it should be considered with the upgrade of the 
		Infrastructure Enhancement of Menoufiya University. The activities of 
		the project are to help the Information &amp; Link Network to establish a 
		robust, standards based infrastructure, including hardware ( powerful 
		Routers, Switches (core, modular, edge, shared switches), Hubs, Modems, 
		Servers, Firewalls, PCs, …etc.), software (latest databases, and web 
		developers software)&nbsp; associated applications, extra, intra, and inter&nbsp; 
		Network Connectivity, and global connectivity through the Internet. 
		Deployment of a high-speed network infrastructure based on international 
		standards at each node of the hole network. The main network principle 
		will be high speed ATM or Gigabit backbone ( E3----------&gt;Gigabit ), 
		modular switches at each faculty, institute, center levels, edge 
		switches at the departments &amp; laboratories level, and shared switches at 
		the libraries and faculty office level.</font></b></p>
		<p class="MsoNormal" dir="LTR" style="text-align: justify; text-kashida: 0%; text-indent: 57.6pt; line-height: 150%; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed">
		<b><font color="#375294">&nbsp;</font></b></p>
		<p class="MsoNormal" dir="LTR" style="text-align: justify; text-kashida: 0%; line-height: 150%; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed">
		<b><font color="#375294">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Finally the main principles of the 
		project are :</font></b></p>
		<p class="MsoNormal" dir="LTR" style="text-align: justify; text-kashida: 0%; line-height: 150%; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed">
		<b><font color="#375294">&nbsp;</font></b></p>
		<p class="MsoNormal" dir="LTR" style="text-align: justify; text-kashida: 0%; text-indent: -20.25pt; line-height: 150%; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; margin-left: 38.25pt; margin-right: 38.25pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: .0001pt">
		<b><font color="#375294">1-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; To enhance and upgrade the 
		infrastructure of the ILN and its branches.</font></b></p>
		<p class="MsoNormal" dir="LTR" style="text-align: justify; text-kashida: 0%; text-indent: -20.25pt; line-height: 150%; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; margin-left: 38.25pt; margin-right: 38.25pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: .0001pt">
		<b><font color="#375294">2-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Simultaneously&nbsp; upgrade the bandwidth 
		of the connectivity&nbsp; between the ILN and FRCU ( E3----Gigabit ).</font></b></p>
		<p class="MsoNormal" dir="LTR" style="text-align: justify; text-kashida: 0%; text-indent: -20.25pt; line-height: 150%; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; margin-left: 38.25pt; margin-right: 38.25pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: .0001pt">
		<b><font color="#375294">3-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Upgrade the extra, intra, and intra 
		links between the ILN and its branches at Shebin El-Kom, Ashemon, 
		Menouf, and Sadat City.</font></b></p>
		<p class="MsoNormal" dir="LTR" style="text-align: justify; text-kashida: 0%; text-indent: -20.25pt; line-height: 150%; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; margin-left: 38.25pt; margin-right: 38.25pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: .0001pt">
		<b><font color="#375294">4-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Connect the Internet to the new 
		faculties, institutes, and centers&nbsp; which are not yet have accessing to 
		the Internet.</font></b></p>
		<p class="MsoNormal" dir="LTR" style="text-align: justify; text-kashida: 0%; text-indent: -20.25pt; line-height: 150%; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; margin-left: 38.25pt; margin-right: 38.25pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: .0001pt">
		<b><font color="#375294">5-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Guarantee to support newly 
		instruments, and services based on the e-technologies.</font></b></p>
		<p class="MsoNormal" dir="LTR" style="text-align: justify; text-kashida: 0%; text-indent: -20.25pt; line-height: 150%; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; margin-left: 38.25pt; margin-right: 38.25pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: .0001pt">
		<b><font color="#375294">6-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Provide security policy and mechanisms 
		to protect the Information Technologies resources of hole ILN and its 
		branches.</font></b></p>
		<p class="MsoNormal" dir="LTR" style="text-align: justify; text-kashida: 0%; text-indent: -20.25pt; line-height: 150%; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; margin-left: 38.25pt; margin-right: 38.25pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: .0001pt">
		<b><font color="#375294">7-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Provide&nbsp; good helps, best services, and 
		guidelines for the end users.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></b></p>
